To reach Bayonne, it’s best to leave your car, if you have one, in one of Biarritz’s large central car parks and catch the A2 bus (every 10 minutes) from beside the Tourist Office in Square d’Ixelles to Place des Basques in the centre of Bayonne. It takes 20 minutes and costs €1.
